exceptions.exn: Unable to apply lemma of type "forall x : nat, a <= x < b -> f x < f (S x)" on hypothesis of type "a <= x < y".
Unable to apply lemma of type "forall x : nat, a <= x -> x < b -> f x < f (S x)" on hypothesis of type "y <= b".

original: intros f b a H x y H0. destruct H0 as [H0 H1]. apply H in H0. apply H in H1. lia.
